ponent-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;了解百思买、塔吉特、沃尔玛等的价格匹配政策&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21570383/price-matching-policy-apple-google-microsoft&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在黑色星期五和网络期间找到最优惠的价格星期一&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21587765/black-friday-cyber-monday-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;3cCHYD&quot;>;随着 11 月 24 日的临近，我们可能会看到更好的优惠，但到目前为止打折的商品仍然值得一看。例如，Apple 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/B0CHWRXH8B?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank &quot;>;配备 USB-C 的更新版 AirPods Pro&lt;/a>; 已经回到了亚马逊最近的 Prime Day 活动期间首次创下的历史最低水平。一系列其他小玩意和小玩意儿也在促销，来自...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech- Deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>